ss=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a843707915ba83a0b5cfd86e3c76b9f2e68799","tid":1524682,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e8d6c19380fe7c6981659d3efb55665db428d4","tid":1524682,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"[最後一着,終極升級,攬炒玉碎]如果想向港鐵公司(0066)及其大股東復仇,麻煩入一入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524655\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524655</a>"},{"pid":"93f0cc5ee592e4c08c2f6884b8defd7fde166df9","tid":1524682,"uid":230472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:00:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53068de07606a019c647b13d0be2b1cdb7381f0b","tid":1524682,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"596525136388749ba8b57a5b4f349d155add7214","tid":1524682,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:52:50.000Z","msg":"831 係市民定畀政府，落實五大訴求既最後機會<br />\n<br />\n今日，佢不但無珍惜呢個機會，而且用殘暴去回應，令無數市民身心受創<br />\n<br />\n因此，香港人從呢一刻起，正式無限期罷工罷課罷市，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">直至新政府成立</span><br />\n<br />\n殘害人民既政權，最終必然滅亡<br />\n<br />\nGod bless Hong Kong"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:02:07.000Z","msg":"罷工罷巿罷課難做？要搵食？<br />\n咁罷買無人阻你啦掛？<br />\n抵制紅媒，唔係咁難掛？<br />\n唔去元朗荃灣北角消費，唔係無可能掛？<br />\n<br />\n唔係要大家都做深山野人！但係，盡做啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n撇除政府問題，淨係計警隊，再淨係計721 85 811 新屋嶺  CCTV直送 831，已經夠哂理由比示威者做任何野，包括以武制暴 以眼還眼 百倍奉還<br />\n<br />\n重申七一宣言，設立死線，立即實行雙普選，垫翻港共政權<br />\n<br />\n「勇武派」、「和理非」係角色，唔係派系，理念一致，只係手法不同<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#重組警隊 刑事追究 改革監警制度<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"7c142d23f2f7567098ec7740fd1038d570ca9f73","tid":1524682,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:04:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即係放棄做中國香港人？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放棄港共政權？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁好"},{"pid":"34da08a886daeea9d9f32dfe774f558ace7b5010","tid":1524682,"uid":300554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">成立臨時政府！<br />\n要有地下組織！<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【升級罷工】EndGame＝全面開啟升級抗爭</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">網民問卷調查報告 我們在這沉痛的晚上公佈</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1525035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1525035</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVP4X9g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVP4X9g.jpg&h=c7d56cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5iA4Pi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5iA4Pi.jpg&h=b866962b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hL7VVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hL7VVY.jpg&h=fc849ad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee56f733a1e9712adec0e4539269aa91e178ad39","tid":1524682,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"512dc8a7b4b5122675911270df921f4915b494ec","tid":1524682,"uid":9256,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:53:33.000Z","msg":"支持，雖然好大機會搞唔成<br />\n<br />\n721 811 831"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:22:00.000Z","msg":"成日話一步步行 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>行啦！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【升級罷工】EndGame＝全面開啟升級抗爭</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold